headline: OSB GROUP PLC - Transaction in Own Shares and Total Voting Rights
summary: OSB GROUP PLC ISIN: GB00BLDRH36002 February 2026 LEI number: 213800ZBKL9BHSL2K459 OSB GROUP PLC (the “Company”) Transaction in Own Shares and Total Voting Rights The Company announces that on 30 January 2026 it had purchased a total of 69,083 of its ordinary shares of £0.01 each (the "ordinary shares") on the London Stock Exchange, CBOE BXE and CBOE CXE, through the Company's broker Citigroup Global Markets Limited as detailed below. The repurchased ordinary shares will be cancelled. London Stoc
